t;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 20 Aug 2009 14:33:34 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/portal/noticias/sun-e-dextra-vao-oferecer-cursos-de-java</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/portal/noticias/sun-e-dextra-vao-oferecer-cursos-de-java</guid></item></channel></rss>